  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a mini casserole over medium heat.",
    "Add the cumin powder, garam masala, paprika, and salt. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chickpeas, cornstarch, water, cilantro, mint, and lemon juice. Mix well.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a preheated tandoor and cook for 15 minutes, or until the cornstarch is cooked and the flavors have melded together.",
    "Drizzle with the grapeseed oil and serve hot.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro and mint, if desired."
  ],
